CustomField.description: The top edge of the zone. This is similar to the y-coordinate, except that position zero starts just below the upper tab bar (i.e. you must subtract the tab bar thickness from Y).
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Enter the position of the top edge of the zone. This value is similar to the y-coordinate, except that position zero starts just below the upper tab bar (i.e. you must subtract the tab bar thickness from Y).
CustomField.label: Top
